00:06.720 --> 00:08.153
You know my skin can't take the sun.

00:08.351 --> 00:10.315
Is there culture here?

00:10.549 --> 00:11.799
Well, there's yoghurt.

00:12.232 --> 00:13.323
Mine's the same.

00:13.589 --> 00:14.948
He won't even go on the window sill.

00:15.243 --> 00:18.445
I want to peel off in the sun but he says he's too hairy.

00:18.887 --> 00:19.383
Definitely.

00:19.693 --> 00:21.677
We should probably go on our own holiday.

00:22.051 --> 00:23.095
That's fine by me.

00:23.233 --> 00:24.051
And me as well.

